Wednesday, December 26, 1990

MERIT DOCKET

90-943. Welch Hills Dev. Corp. v. Franklin Cty. Bd. of Revision.

Board of Tax Appeals, Nos. 89-F-257, 89-C-257, 89-F-258 and 89-C-258. On motion to dismiss and on motion to consolidate with 90-1409, Greenleaf Investment Corp. v. Franklin Cty. Bd. of Revision, Board of Tax Appeals, No. 89-G-243; 90-1410, HWK Corp. v. Franklin Cty. Bd. of Revision, Board of *711Tax Appeals, No. 89-A-246; 90-1411, HWK Corp. v. Franklin Cty. Bd. of Revision, Board of Tax Appeals, No. 89-A-248; 90-1412, Greenleaf Investment Corp. v. Franklin Cty. Bd. of Revision, Board of Tax Appeals, No. 89-G-244; and 90-1413, WKH Corp. v. Franklin Cty. Bd. of Revision, Board of Tax Appeals, Nos. 89-F-252, 89- F-253, 89-F-254, 89-F-255 and 89-F-256. Motion to dismiss granted; motion to consolidate granted; sua sponte, case Nos. 90-1409, 90-1410, 90-1411, 90-1412 and 90- 1413 are dismissed.

Moyer, C.J., Sweeney, Holmes, Douglas, Wright, H. Brown and Resnick, JJ., concur.
